{"tid":1990946,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"在全日本有約40間分店的商務旅館集團WBF，今天宣布已申請民事再生，即日起由政府監管。","createTime":"2020-04-27T05:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T07:31:47.000Z","uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"832822beb86d566bb28e5ea5cd59d406c25b7cc3","tid":1990946,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:48:13.000Z","msg":"在全日本有約40間分店的商務旅館集團WBF(WBFホテル＆リゾーツ)，今天宣布已申請民事再生，即日起由政府監管。<br />\n<br />\n所有集團直營旅館已停業，而由集團其他分公司開設的旅館及設施(WBFリゾート沖縄株式会社等)則暫時維持正常。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，公司集團現時負債達180億円，是 #新型コロナウイルス 相關破產公司中最大規模的一間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://airstair.jp/wbf-hotel-resorts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fairstair.jp%2Fwbf-hotel-resorts%2F&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4E8L9AbO9EvXEPTzVQ1jYSs%3D&h=5e5c72f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://airstair.jp/wbf-hotel-resorts/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pix10.agoda.net/hotelImages/2962076/-1/82853c2150ca4a4155fca65a71e560a3.jpg?s=1024x768\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpix10.agoda.net%2FhotelImages%2F2962076%2F-1%2F82853c2150ca4a4155fca65a71e560a3.jpg%3Fs%3D1024x768&h=ab36534f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3fd02dd64563d49052123bd1965fa756a76ce50c","tid":1990946,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:48:55.000Z","msg":"民事再生法設立之目的在於日本企業面臨破產的威脅時，債務人可在法院的介入下，於短期間之內得到一定人數債權人的同意，免除大部分之債務或以分期支付的方式清償債務，以進行企業整頓，有重整或清算等意思"},{"pid":"14b5b88efa6aab8cf27fecbf6dd2e3140f06d7eb","tid":1990946,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135fcc6f9c9b10ab919c926eb27077e45b772b66","tid":1990946,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b5b88efa6aab8cf27fecbf6dd2e3140f06d7eb","tid":1990946,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"其他地方唔報姐"},{"pid":"deab34844f9b9b77149204badd5ff7eaa9e2b27f","tid":1990946,"uid":246295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"135fcc6f9c9b10ab919c926eb27077e45b772b66","tid":1990946,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b5b88efa6aab8cf27fecbf6dd2e3140f06d7eb","tid":1990946,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"其他地方唔報姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T06:57:26.000Z","msg":"日本特別嚴重都係真既<br />\n有唔少旅遊業相關為左奧運做左expansion<br />\n結果依家咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3b56203ef51810025c5074ecdf138a2c9afe6e","tid":1990946,"uid":325586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T06:59:44.000Z","msg":"為左奧運開多左,同埋連自己國內旅遊客都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"290fd6e3f29549d176ca4c92b9ee720470fec266","tid":1990946,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-27T07:31:47.000Z","msg":"又一間"}]}